  "title": "Potion Recipes: Dark Mode Edition!",
  "description": "NOW IN DARK MODE! All possible potion recipes on the brewing stand UI!",
  "body": "<center>\n\n![Potion_Recipes_Dark_Mode_Edition_Banner](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5f8bfeaba547915c4873b4b3e6b01b3ca3ca4beb_0.webp)\n\n  \n**¡Hola! ~ Welcome to Potion Recipes: Dark Mode Edition!**\n\nThanks to this resource pack, you’ll not only get extra help when brewing your own potions, but you’ll also <br> avoid eye strain in the process. Here you'll be able to choose which \"edition\" you'd like to play, this resouce <br> pack is just a dark mode of the original resource packs I've made, but also the ones yet to come.\n\nAll the help you need, right in the brewing stand UI!\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/pixelforge\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/32237a5eb0e69b0cfb6f79b09d08bafae2139664.png\" alt=\"Modrinth\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/shadows_pixelforge\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6f8e5473c7cc891773d0963a204a7dbc0cae6ab8.png\" alt=\"Ko-fi\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://discord.gg/QrU6QCFj5r\"> \n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/ab1d9434d86f69f02be997775cc20d9f968fc6a6.png\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/shadowspixelforge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fc15ed1de151999554a0a966e39ccaef439d6d4d.png\" alt=\"Twitch\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/shadowspixelforge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/2f10668a84476def0faf37c42319e0222484f94d.png\" alt=\"Instagram\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/c/shadowspixelforge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b10f11429c9b97af2b45fcda64792d815fdeb5fb.png\" alt=\"Patreon\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/shadowspixelforge/projects\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6aa1b4a7d469617ce0e922b931c24e73ef48dc59.png\" alt=\"Curseforge\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC3qlCr9lXguH44qq5xqAlzQ\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/74af846b0dabfde51cc50f295809ec96f63e26a2.png\" alt=\"Youtube\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://x.com/SPixelForge\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/eb699f87a889d2710efc5dcff9b6b023b2be2d58.png\" alt=\"X\" width=\"55\" height=\"50\"> </a>\n<br><br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/50c52f0c97dcb0cfff794cbc83043630a4942f8b.png\" alt=\"hr\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a2f227dd350f4e2322f500900863b7a6696b74f7.png\" alt=\"NO DEPENDENCIES REQUIRED\" width=\"660\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n  **This resource pack works perfectly with Vanilla Minecraft - NO EXTRA MODS REQUIRED.** \n\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/50c52f0c97dcb0cfff794cbc83043630a4942f8b.png\" alt=\"hr\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/4410885464b2b5fa29b5265dd3057ad7cb425be9.png\" alt=\"OG\" width=\"790\" height=\"50\">\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/potion-recipes-vanilla-edition!\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/b005be988fcfc7850e57a395c0b461ca4d08601b.png\" alt=\"Potion Recipes: Vanilla Edition\" width=\"700\" height=\"50\"> </a>\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/potion-recipes-pixels-reforged-edition!\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/8df53510ad8d62b7bfade45498d0c4505dfedc43_0.webp\" alt=\"Potion Recipes: Pixels Reforged Edition\" width=\"700\" height=\"50\"> </a>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/50c52f0c97dcb0cfff794cbc83043630a4942f8b.png\" alt=\"hr\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/c7f3b2837c699bc40bda584b7d5781389c4dbe3d.png\" alt=\"MORE INTERESTING PROJECTS\" width=\"690\" height=\"50\">\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"20\">\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/shadows-pixels-reforged\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/81c5b3f05c13dac83081221b58110365ada040c7_0.webp\" alt=\"Pixels Reforged\" width=\"200\"></a><br>\n      Pixels Reforged\n    </td>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/the-night-of-the-living-pumpkins\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/243c0c1904de2361e931432a6e0e5b0ee6b27e8f.png\" alt=\"The Night of the <br> Living Pumpkins! Icon\" width=\"200\"></a><br>\n      The Night of the <br> Living Pumpkins! <br>\n    </td>\n    <td align=\"center\">\n      <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/datapack/railbalance\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/a3a7175ae8324de3de9cbfd3c3032780e5c9779a_0.webp\" alt=\"Railbalance Icon\" width=\"200\"></a><br>\n      Railbalance\n    </td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/50c52f0c97dcb0cfff794cbc83043630a4942f8b.png\" alt=\"hr\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/5f88863218a1c549051bc37c2cbd07a395d1bdd2.png\" alt=\"YOUR SUPPORT MAKES THE DIFFERENCE\" width=\"850\" height=\"50\">\n<br>\n<br>\nIf you like the content I make, don’t hesitate to join my Patreon or Ko-fi to enjoy all the exclusive members-only content, you'll get access to a lot of bonus content like WIPs, making ofs, dev. blogs and much more!\n<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/shadows_pixelforge/tiers\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/6dc8719629fd05f40aba4f4e58bc56458925abae.png\" alt=\"join ko-fi\" width=\"400\" height=\"50\"> </a> <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/shadowspixelforge/membership\"> <img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e73a4a0852508cb8d2b6a3dae2a42baef09334c0.png\" alt=\"join patreon\" width=\"400\" height=\"50\"> </a> \n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/50c52f0c97dcb0cfff794cbc83043630a4942f8b.png\" alt=\"hr\" width=\"900\" height=\"50\">\n\n<br>\n<br>\n\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/fb424f5c7e4031e9d8691616a446883413c75421.png\" alt=\"FAQs\" width=\"155\" height=\"50\">\n\n</center>\n<br>\n<br>\n\nHere I leave some answers to a few possible questions you may have, I hope it can help you.\n\n<details>\n  <summary>Frequently Asked Questions</summary>\n\n> **Q: Is Potion Recipes: Dark Mode Edition a Mod / Modpack / Data Pack / Plugin...?**\n> \n> A: No, this is just a resource pack!\n\n> **Q: Can you / Will you make a Bedrock port?**\n> \n> A: To make a version that would work on Bedrock, I would need to learn how Bedrock works. So that's not something I plan to do any time soon for now, but it will come eventually.\n\n> **Q: Do you / Will you ever make a Mod?**\n> \n> A: For now we are mostly working on resource packs, follow us on ko-fi or patreon to stay up to date.\n\n> **Q: Can I put your resource pack in my Modpack?**\n> \n> A: Yes, you can do it as long as you give us credit.\n\n> **Q: Will you add more \"dark mode\" editions over time?**\n> \n> A: Yes, the idea is having a dark mode variant for every single potion recipes edition.\n\n\n</details>",
